    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this one go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is an absolute gem\u2014it\u2019s been kept in a climate-controlled garage and looks just as stunning as the day it was first bought. The interior is spotless, the paint is gleaming, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been truly pampered and feels brand new, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
      "price": 45500.0,
