    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather. This example is powered by the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double VANOS, delivering a linear power band to an 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanically, this chassis is superlative: the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the rod bearing service is documented. Power is transmitted via a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a 3.62 limited-slip differential. The suspension retains its factory geometry with refreshed bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers, ensuring optimal turn-in and lateral stability. Rolling on forged Style 67 wheels wrapped in fresh Michelin rubber, this M3 exhibits zero oxidation and factory-spec compression across all cylinders. A true turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
