    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute gem for the discerning collector or enthusiast. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously garage-kept and climate-controlled since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with zero swirls, chips, or imperfections, protected by a high-end ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in a 'time-capsule' state; the premium leather is supple with no bolster wear, and the buttons still have that crisp, new-car tactile feel. Mechanically, it is flawless. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with a comprehensive folder of records included. No leaks, no noises, and a drive that is as tight and responsive as the day it rolled off the assembly line. This is a rare opportunity to own a truly preserved example that needs absolutely nothing but a new home.",
      "price": 46500.0,
