      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this one go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy this absolute beauty. It\u2019s in truly flawless shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, keeping it spotless and perfectly maintained. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the new-car price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
