      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2004 Honda S2000 (AP2) in showroom-fresh condition. This example features the high-revving F22C1 2.2L DOHC VTEC inline-four, delivering linear power delivery and a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis maintains its factory structural rigidity with all original VIN tags present on every panel. Mechanically flawless, it boasts a precise 6-speed close-ratio manual transmission and a Torsen limited-slip differential for optimal torque biasing. The double-wishbone suspension remains tight, providing telepathic handling characteristics. Finished in Berlina Black with a pristine interior showing zero bolster wear, this S2000 is a rare, unmolested specimen for the discerning purist.",
